V`60)
X`09echo`20"`60date`60`20`20badaddr`09`09$rp`09$to"`20>>`20../ldbstarter.log
X`09mail`20-s`20"Mail`20to`20invalid`20ldb`20address"`20$rp:q`20<<EOF
X
